oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Grand ole opry (Radio program); Tubb, Ernest, 1914-1984; Cargill, Henson;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and black on white) Hatch poster announcing Grand Ole Opry stars Ernest Tubb and the Text Troubadours with Joe and Rose Lee, Maphis, Billye Raye Lankford, Henson Cargill and Mary Taylor. Poster features a metal photoplate of Ernest Tubb, Henson Gargill, Joe and Rose Lee, and Maphis.
